FBIS4-46171 "jptot022__l94080" JPRS-TOT-94-022-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 27 May 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA `Terrorists' Seize 30 Hostages on Board Bus in North Caucasus `Terrorists' Seize 30 Hostages on Board Bus in North Caucasus Hostages Free; Fourth Kidnapper Killed LD2705101694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0940 GMT 27 May 94 LD2705101694 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow May 27 TASS -- The fourth hostage-taker was killed by a special task force, according to unconfirmed reports. Reliable sources told TASS that the money and weapons given to the terrorists remained in the helicopter. The anti-terrorist operation, held near the Chechen settlement of Bacha-Yurt where the helicopter with terrorists landed, freed all hostages unharmed.
